body:
This Comeback

On Bangtan’s end this comeback has been a blesssing they have released an amazing album with amazing songs and themes and everything is truly beautiful and amazing.

But,

The fans have been terrible. People are obsessed with lines more than ever, the expectations have been raised to an impossible standard and now today. I love bangtan and I truly enjoy spending time with a lot of people within this fandom, but this comeback has made me ashamed to call myself a part of a group like this.

Just please take a step back and evaluate what it is you’re trying to accomplish with what you are saying.

title: BTS IS GOING TO BE IN THE RDMAS!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
body: I just found out when I went to vote for the RDMAS (Radio Disney Music Awards) that BTS is nominated for 4 awards! The awards they’re nominated for are: Fiercest fans (BTS Army), Best song that made you smile (DNA), Best dance track(Mic drop [Steve Aoki remix]), and Best duo/group. My fellow ARMIES, get to voting! All voting ends on June 3rd, so we don’t have much time! Let’s help our boys get the awards they deserve!
